ibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1916 166 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001701</a>  </li><li> Bitto 2001 14 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000029</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Large deep letters, with slight tendency to extensions/serifs at stroke ends. Borken bar alpha (but also straight on line 2), lunate sigma, regular epsilon, use of ligature.</p> Line 1-4  40-43  Interlineation line 1 to 4  4-6  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
